fields.title: mobile exploration lab,  50362-0
fields.history_note:
References: Micronauts

Mobile Exploration Lab including Extra Capsule Vehicle, Safety Missile Launcher, Rocket Jet Base, Observation Dome, Mechanical Arms.   Over 13in tall and is interchangeable with all micronauts figures and playset accessories included allow you to change the mobile exploration lab to many different vehicles.
